        "text": "Since 1987, The Legal 500 has been analyzing the capabilities of law firms around the world, with a comprehensive research program revised and updated annually to present the most up-to-date vision of the global market. Based in London, England, The Legal 500 assesses the strengths of law firms in more than 150 jurisdictions. These rankings are based on a series of criteria that highlights the practice area teams who provide some of the most innovative legal advice to clients and outside corporate counsel. Annually, their research is based on feedback from more than 300,000 clients worldwide, submissions from law firms, interviews with leading private practice attorneys, and leading researchers with unparalleled experience in the legal market."
