        "text": "Founded in 1979, Riley Bennett Egloff’s attorneys are committed to assisting their clients in identifying their objectives, evaluating available alternatives in light of the pertinent legal environment, and aggressively pursuing those objectives. Our lawyers are frequently called upon to litigate cases throughout Indiana and across the country. We provide services in a number of different areas not typically found in mid-sized Indianapolis law firms."
