        "text": "Through the support of the Lilly Endowment, United Way’s Capital Projects Fund has provided grants totaling $147.5 million since 2000. The fund has enabled United Way to invest in 146 projects for 73 agencies. For every $1 that United Way invests in projects, the fund helps generate another $2 in broader community support for a total impact of more than $350 million in renovations, new construction and purchases.",
